eu.trentorise.opendata.semtext

Class Meaning

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.opendata.semtext.Meaning
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasMetadata, Serializable, Comparable<Meaning>

    @Immutable
@ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
public final class Meaning
extends Object
implements Comparable<Meaning>, Serializable, HasMetadata
    Represents a meaning along with its probability. Equality is checked only considering the id and meaning kind.
    Author:
    David Leoni
